            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Sri Lankan-style chicken curry </strong>with the <strong>baked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish the curry with the <strong>remaining sliced green chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Dig in! </p>",
